    "ts_title": "Adult ESOL Class",
    "ts_body": "<p>The library offers free ESOL classes for beginners learning English.</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e754f65162db02a2a8a7245d7cc7d5180\">Classes meet every week</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecd36ba902869a2723e7587204f8ea534\">Improve your English</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9b170f6882fae6fca782ddcc60b4fe75\">Practice with other adults learning English</li></ul><p><strong>This class is first-come, first-served until classroom hits capacity. We recommend arriving a few minutes early to sign in.&nbsp;</strong></p><p><em>(For non-beginner&nbsp;classes, integrated English literacy, please visit&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://www.bklynlibrary.org/adult-learning/esol\"><em>https://www.bklynlibrary.org/adult-learning/esol</em></a><em>)</em></p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
