    "is_author": 413378,
    "ts_title": "The Cycle Alliance's Period Pantry at Sunset Park!",
    "ts_body": "<p>Do you have a uterus or know somebody with one? Are you a teen who would like to learn more about or experiment with unfamiliar menstrual products? Stop by the Period Pantry at Sunset Park, and grab a care package, complete with a variety of menstrual hygiene products brought to you by community donations.</p><p>Located in the Young Adult Area, Open <strong>Monday-Saturday during branch open hours</strong>.</p><p>This is open to <strong>all ages</strong> and <strong>genders!</strong> Patrons are encouraged to donate to our pantry for all teens regardless of gender identity and sexual orientation. Adults who need the pantry are also welcomed to take and donate.&nbsp;</p><p>In-kind donations can be brought to the branch or check out our wishlist: <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/hz/wishlist/ls/1UAJ05OYOICX3?ref_=wl_share\">https://www.amazon.com/hz/wishlist/ls/1UAJ05OYOICX3?ref_=wl_share</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
