    "item_id": "815829",
    "is_author": 375774,
    "ts_title": "Free Intermediate English Class (We Speak NYC) ",
    "ts_body": "<p><span>The library offers free English classes for<strong> intermediate-level English speakers</strong> looking to continue their education.</span></p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb0ac8a15455d3da7135f7220cc981f4f\"><span>Classes meet once a week.</span></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e96c2e91bebd2a6dc5bfe3ad8f283f887\"><span>Practice and improve your English with other adults.</span></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9bf720d1b1f484fcf18cd2de205c47ee\"><span>Watch We Speak NYC videos and learn about City services.</span></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e016d12fe0e85028deacaac030cec61ba\"><span>Get information on rights and resources for immigrant&nbsp;New&nbsp;Yorkers.</span></li></ul><p><span>No registration required!</span></p><p><span><strong>Please note: This is an intermediate-level class for students who already possess some English language skills.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://static.bklynlibrary.org/prod/public/inline-images/royal%20blue%20MOIA%20Horizontal%20Logo_Final_2-01%20%28003%29.png\" data-entity-uuid=\"787b8384-57b6-496d-80f1-41ea412aa464\" data-entity-type=\"file\" alt=\"NYC MOIA \" width=\"306\" height=\"84\"></p>",
