    "item_id": "817305",
    "is_author": 232981,
    "ts_title": "Free English Class (We Speak NYC)",
    "ts_body": "<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:proxima-nova, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The library offers free ESOL classes for <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:proxima-nova-bold, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:bolder;\">intermediate </strong>students learning English.&nbsp;</p><ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:proxima-nova, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;padding-left:2rem;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\" data-list-item-id=\"e24ea12d7ffca3359ac1c5536f3399e9b\">Classes meet every week</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\" data-list-item-id=\"ed7f236752b2e8341a8f2da0c9f5b24fc\">Improve your English</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\" data-list-item-id=\"ed25bcf630584c19e1d85f63caf4cc3f9\">Practice with other adults learning English</li></ul><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:proxima-nova, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:proxima-nova-bold, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:bolder;\">This class is first-come, first-served until classroom hits capacity.&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:proxima-nova, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">(For non-beginner&nbsp;classes, integrated English literacy, or classes&nbsp;outside of Sheepeshead Bay, please visit&nbsp;</em><a style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(72, 78, 128);text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"https://www.bklynlibrary.org/adult-learning/esol\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">https://www.bklynlibrary.org/adult-learning/esol</em></a><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">)</em></p>",
